<refsect1>
  <title>About this document</title>
  <para>This document shows milters reported that they are works with milter manager.</para>
  <para>
  Milters that not listed here will be able to work with milter manager. If you can work a milter not listed here with milter manager, please report the milter to 
  <ulink url='https://lists.sourceforge.net/lists/listinfo/milter-manager-users-en'>mailing list</ulink>
  .
</para>
</refsect1>

